      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CAWBOURNE LADY (8) recorded a Mix win two back then missed the frame last time at this track, but drawn Box 8 this time where she has won before. Better than latest and can atone here. MAXIMUM DAMAGE (2) has a strong record this track and trip with two wins and two placings from six starts. In the money last time at this track (30.66) in a NG, finishing a 2 length third. With even luck and a clean start can sneak into the finish. CAWBOURNE CALI (4) had been racing well with a Grade 5 win three back then placed next time before missing the frame latest at this track. Expected to bounce back to best. PHOENIX VIOLET (5) was in the money last start and wasn't beaten far - poses a threat again.",
